% EMBC 2006) could not be located in IEEE Xplore or any other
% database. The "bias cancellation" methodology cited at the three
% original use sites is actually published in PMID 18779073
% (Sriraam + Eswaran, "An Adaptive Error Modeling Scheme for the
% Lossless Compression of EEG Signals", IEEE TITB 12(5):587-594,
% 2008), already represented as `sriraam2007` below. All three
% `\cite{sriram2006}` sites in the .tex have been retargeted to
% `sriraam2007`, and the phantom entry was removed.

% NOTE: cite key reads `sriraam2007` for historical reasons; actual
% publication year is 2008 (see year field). All `\cite{sriraam2007}`
% sites in the .tex resolve to this entry. The paper introduces the
% context-based bias-cancellation scheme cited at §II.E and §III.B.
